<title>hllwyạ tgẖlbt ʿly̱ ạlkẖṭyẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- hllwyạ tgẖlbt ʿly̱ ạlkẖṭyẗ hllwyạ
 tgẖlbt bạ̹lhy fy
 1- yftḥ kwy̱ ạlsmạʾ yʿṭyny qwẗ
 yftḥ kwy̱ ạlsmạʾ yʿṭyny brkạt
 yftḥ kwy̱ ạlsmạʾ ymlạ̉ny bạlḥyạẗ
 2- knt ạ̉nẓr llkẖṭyẗ wạ̉nạ ʿṭsẖạn
 fṣrkẖt lạ̹lhy bqlb ḥyrạn qlt lh ạ̉njdny
 3- ạ̉ʿṭạny tsbyḥh ṣrkẖt lh bhạ
 ạ̉ʿṭạny tsbyḥẗ fkkt qydy bhạ ạ̉ʿṭạny tsbyḥ</lyrics>
</song>